#

Italian Herb Dressing

5 min
$2.5
90 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

DressingItalianSauce

Description

A vibrant and zesty dressing perfect for salads, pasta, or drizzling over grilled vegetables.

Ingredients

  • olive oil: 1/2 cup
  • red wine vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • dijon mustard: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • dried oregano: 1 teaspoon
  • dried basil: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
  • fresh parsley, chopped: 2 tablespoons
